<!--
  English string resources (default language).

  Mirrors the Themes/*.xaml pattern: this ResourceDictionary is swapped into
  Application.Resources by LocalizationService, and every localized string is
  referenced from XAML via {DynamicResource Str.<Area>.<Name>} so a language
  change updates the UI live. C# reads strings via ILocalizationService.Get(key).

  Key convention:  Str.<Area>.<Name>   e.g. Str.Common.Cancel, Str.Dashboard.Title
  To add a language: copy this file to Strings/<culture>.xaml, translate the
  values (keep the keys), and add it to GlobalOptionsViewModel.LanguageOptions.
-->
